claim.claim-text:
Shoe according to one of patent claims 2 to 4, characterized in that the shoe additionally has an insole, wherein the insole has a flat back side in direction of the outsole of the shoe and a dome-shaped structure on the front side, characterized in that
- the dome-shaped structure (18) has a base surface of a maximum of 15% of the insole surface;
- the dome-shaped structure (18) is positioned under the cuboid bone (4) of the shoe wearer.
